  "notes": "Born 1580 in London, England. Father: Sir James Taylor (1550-1627). Married Sir Robert Rogers. Daughter Anne Rogers (1590-1633). Son Thomas John Rogers (1609-1670). Husband Sir Robert died 1639 in Hatton. Cecelia emigrated to colonial Massachusetts — died June 3, 1662 in Watertown, Middlesex County at age 82. Buried July 19, 1667 at Kirkleatham, Yorkshire, England (body returned to England?)."
